<h1>Post</h1>

<p>According to an Adrenaline Vault <a href="http://www.avault.com/news/displaynews.asp?story=11122004-85036">story</a>, Marvel is suing NCsoft and Cryptic Studios because of their MMORPG, City of Heroes. Why? &quot;Marvel claims that that the game allows players to create characters which are too similar to the Hulk, X-Men, and other heroes from their comic book series, violating their trademarks.&quot;</p>
<p>In related news, Marvel also announced suits against major paper and pen manufacturers, as well as Crayola and various paint companies.</p>
}